Check outliers call

metabolon %>%
  head(500) %>% 
  ggplot( ) +
  geom_point( aes(x = name,
              y = value,
              color = outliers)) +
  facet_wrap( phenotype~BIOCHEMICAL, scales = "free" )
metabolon %>%
  ## add metadata for covariates 
  dplyr::left_join(
    metadata_metabolon,
    by = c( "name" = "ID")
  ) %>% 
  mutate(
    scaled_value = scale(value, center = median(value), scale = T),
    phenotype = phenotype %>% 
      as.factor() %>% 
      `levels<-`(c("blueprint","smim"))
  ) %>% 
  dplyr::group_map(
    .data = .,
    ~ glm(
      data = .,
      formula = scaled_value ~ phenotype + GENDER + Smoker + Smoker_past + Alcohol + AGE + BMI
    ) %>%
      broom::tidy() %>%
      dplyr::mutate(
        BIOCHEMICAL = .x %>% dplyr::filter(phenotype == "blueprint") %$% BIOCHEMICAL %>% unique(),
        SUPER_PATHWAY = .x %>% dplyr::filter(phenotype == "blueprint") %$% SUPER_PATHWAY %>% unique(),
        SUB_PATHWAY = .x %>% dplyr::filter(phenotype == "blueprint") %$% SUB_PATHWAY %>% unique(),
        KEGG = .x %>% dplyr::filter(phenotype == "blueprint") %$% KEGG %>% unique()
      ),
    .keep = T
  ) %>%
  data.table::rbindlist() %>%
  dplyr::filter(term != "(Intercept)") %>%
  dplyr::mutate(FDR = p.adjust(p = `p.value`,
                               method = 'fdr')) -> stat_df

stat_df %>% 
  dplyr::filter(term == "phenotypesmim") %>% 
  arrange( FDR ) %>% 
  readr::write_csv("Analysis_metabolon_20230119.csv", 
                   append = F, 
                   col_names = T, 
                   quote = 'all', 
                   num_threads = 3 )
stat_df %>% 
  left_join(
    smim_metabolon,
    by = "BIOCHEMICAL" 
    ) %$%
  SUPER_PATHWAY.y -> stat_df$SUPER_PATHWAY

stat_df %>% 
    dplyr::filter(term == "phenotypesmim") %>% 
  filter( !is.na(SUPER_PATHWAY) ) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_point(aes(
    x = estimate,
    y = -log(FDR),
    color = SUPER_PATHWAY
  ))

metabolon %>%
  ## add metadata for covariates 
  dplyr::left_join(
    metadata_metabolon,
    by = c( "name" = "ID")
  ) %>% 
  mutate(
    scaled_value = scale(value, center = median(value), scale = T),
    phenotype = phenotype %>% 
      as.factor() %>% 
      `levels<-`(c("blueprint","smim"))
    ) %>%
  dplyr::group_map(
    .data = .,
    ~ t.test(x = .x[which(.x$phenotype == 'blueprint'), ]$scaled_value,
             y = .x[which(.x$phenotype == 'smim'), ]$scaled_value) %>%
      broom::tidy() %>%
      dplyr::mutate(
        BIOCHEMICAL = .x %>% dplyr::filter(phenotype == "blueprint") %$% BIOCHEMICAL %>% unique(),
        SUPER_PATHWAY = .x %>% dplyr::filter(phenotype == "blueprint") %$% SUPER_PATHWAY %>% unique(),
        SUB_PATHWAY = .x %>% dplyr::filter(phenotype == "blueprint") %$% SUB_PATHWAY %>% unique(),
        KEGG = .x %>% dplyr::filter(phenotype == "blueprint") %$% KEGG %>% unique()
      ),
    .keep = T
  ) %>%
  data.table::rbindlist() %>%
  dplyr::mutate(FDR = p.adjust(p = `p.value`,
                               method = 'fdr')) -> stat_df

stat_df %>% 
  arrange(FDR) %>%
  dplyr::left_join(
    conv_table,
    by = "BIOCHEMICAL"
  ) %>% 
  readr::write_csv("Analysis_metabolon_20230119_ttest.csv", 
                   append = F, 
                   col_names = T, 
                   quote = 'all', 
                   num_threads = 3 )

PCA

metabolon %>% 
  tidyr::pivot_wider( id_cols = c(BIOCHEMICAL), 
                      names_from = name, 
                      values_from = value ) -> df_metabolon_for_PCA

df_metabolon_for_PCA %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  select(2:ncol(.)) %>% 
  as.matrix() -> mtx_metabolon_for_PCA
rownames(mtx_metabolon_for_PCA) <- df_metabolon_for_PCA$BIOCHEMICAL

cor(mtx_metabolon_for_PCA %>% t()) %>%
    caret::findCorrelation() -> row_remove 

mtx_metabolon_for_PCA  <- mtx_metabolon_for_PCA[-row_remove,]
metadata <- data.frame(
  row.names = colnames(mtx_metabolon_for_PCA))
metadata$Group <- case_when( 
  colnames(mtx_metabolon_for_PCA) %in% colnames(control_blueprint_metabolon) ~"blueprint",
  colnames(mtx_metabolon_for_PCA) %in% colnames(smim_metabolon) ~"smim" )
PCAtools::pca(mtx_metabolon_for_PCA, 
              center = T, 
              scale = T,

              metadata = metadata ) -> pca_metabolon
